<text>Louis Schweitzer is the name of:

*Louis Schweitzer (businessman) (born 1942), chairman and former CEO of Renault
*Louis Schweitzer (philanthropist) (1899–1971), paper industrialist and philanthropist, donated WBAI to Pacifica Radio</text><links>
<link wikidata="Q1384681" start="35" end="65" title="Louis Schweitzer (businessman)" label="Louis Schweitzer (businessman)"/>
